        <head>LEWD THINKERS</head>
        <p>According to <name type="law"><rs reg="United States Penal Code, Section 211">Section 211 (as amended by the act of March 4, 1911) of the
            Criminal Code of the <place>United States</place> of America</rs></name>, the expressed
            views concerning birth control of the following thinkers would have been adjudged lewd,
            obscene, filthy, vile and indecent and would have been adjudged against the peace of the
            United States and their dignity.</p>
